data.enText: moving around in the same direction as the hands of a clock

simple_means.memory_skill: clock 时钟 + wise 方向，方式，状态 → 顺时针地

tr: in the same direction as the rotating hands of a clock
in the direction that the hands of a clock move
example: please move clockwise in a circle

value.def: When something is moving clockwise, it is moving in a circle in the same direction as the hands on a clock.

example.ex: He told the children to start moving clockwise around the room.
example.tran: 他让孩子们开始按顺时针方向绕着房间走。

example.ex: Gently swing your right arm in a clockwise direction.
example.tran: 按顺时针方向轻轻摆动右臂。
